sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User as Dashboard User
    participant UI as Streamlit Dashboard
    participant DB as SQLite Core DB

    User->>UI: Open dashboard and select symbol
    UI->>DB: Query available symbols from mart views
    DB-->>UI: Symbol list
    UI-->>User: Render selector

    User->>UI: Choose symbol
    UI->>DB: Query price curve 24h (selected symbol)
    DB-->>UI: Time-series points
    UI-->>User: Render line chart

    UI->>DB: Query price deviation daily (latest day, selected symbol)
    DB-->>UI: Deviation KPI snapshot
    UI-->>User: Render deviation metrics/table

    UI->>DB: Query platform quality daily (latest day)
    DB-->>UI: Latency/disconnect/update KPIs by exchange
    UI-->>User: Render quality table/charts
